== Kaminuza yijyenga ya Kigali ==
[[Kigali Independent University|Kaminuza yijyenga ya Kigali]] (ULK) ni kaminuza yashinzwe mu mwaka wi 1996 ni ishuri rimwe<ref>https://www.4icu.org/reviews/universities-urls/13879.shtm</ref>

mu mashuri makuru ryigenga mu [[Rwanda]]. ni rimwe mu mashuri kandi afite abanyeshuri batari bake

muri [[Kaminuza y'u Rwanda|kaminuza]] ziri m' [[Umujyi wa Kigali]]. ULK kandi afite amashami menshi atandukanye<ref>https://web.facebook.com/ulk.ac.rw/?_rdc=1&_rdr</ref>

== Amateka ==
[[Kigali Independent University|Kaminuza yigenga ya Kigali]] ( ULK) nkuko twa bibonye haruguru yashinzwe tariki 15 werurwe 1996

nyuma ya [[Genocide mu Rwanda|Genocide]] yakorewe abatutsi mu [[Rwanda]]. yatangiye ikorera mu nyubako ya [[Mutagatifu Pawulo]]

ULK kandi yaje kubaka inyubako zayo zambere mu [[Umurenge wa Kacyiru|murenge wa Kacyiru]] aho yaje kuhahindura amashuri

yisumbuye azwi na Glory secondary school. 2007 nibwo ulk yimuriye ibikorwa byayo bya Kminuza

mu murenge wa Gisozi aho yari imaze kubaka inyubako nshyashya.<ref>https://www.4icu.org/reviews/universities-urls/13879.shtm</ref> iyi Kaminuza kandi yashinzwe na 

prof Rwigamba Balinda mu rwego rwo gufasha urubyiruko rwu [[Rwanda]] kuzamura ireme ry' uburezi.

ndetse ni iterambere ry'igihugu cyu [[Rwanda]]

